 1","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Ejemplo 1 del contexto de apilamiento","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Exemple d'empilement 1","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"重ね合わせコンテキストの例 1","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"쌓임 맥락 예제1","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Stacking context example 1","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/css/css_positioning/understanding_z_index/stacking_context_example_1","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/css/css_positioning/understanding_z_index/stacking_context_example_1/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS","title":"CSS（层叠样式表）"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Positioning","title":"CSS Positioning"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Positioning/Understanding_z_index","title":"理解 CSS 的 z-index 属性"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Positioning/Understanding_z_index/Stacking_context_example_1","title":"Stacking context example 1"}],"pageTitle":"Stacking context example 1 - CSS（层叠样式表） | MDN","noIndexing":false}}